Procedure.description:
Procedure Purpose: FCI Resume Scan
Procedure Version: 1 Responsibility: Claudia Tranquilli Last Modified Date: 03.08.2022 Change History:
Version 1: (CT - 03.08.2022) - Procedure created to resume WP; - Procedure Description field updated according to EUMETSAT template.
Procedure Objectives:
- This procedure allows resuming scan after stopping the WP. The scan can be resumed with the pre-loaded REPSEQ.
Procedure Overview:
This procedure can perform the following activities: - Select the MS, SSL and REPSEQ and starts the WP.
Procedure Pre-conditions: S/C in FPM/NOM
Procedure Constraints: None
Spacecraft Configuration: FPM/NOM
Ground Segment Configuration: None
Remarks: PAFs for the update of MS, REPSEQ and INSTCONF are required.
